window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Second World is a mire of intrigue; the game's creators have left several back doors permitting them to terminate anyone at will, and an unlikely sequence of events has brought someone unsuspecting into their field of attention. </p> <p>One player has managed to upset the game world's balance, and now he's hunted by everyone. Every clan wants to recruit him for his achievements while other powers want him for their own, more sinister purposes. Now Ros must contend against an unseen enemy backed by the world's most powerful corporation while relying on only himself and his few trusted allies. The stakes have never been higher.... </p> <p>Don't miss the final book in The Weirdest Noob trilogy! </p>"; 
